{"tid":2122627,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"SWIFT：人民幣國際化正在加速 升至全球第五大最活躍貨幣","createTime":"2020-07-24T05:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T06:10:05.000Z","uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5220c8075d598ce1e4d4d9efcd474318eff5c888","tid":2122627,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20160111/145249980956936361744dd.jpg/4pNWMDBP4RGolWCRuyEcsphE09emhZpy84KBZ_OCgWc?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20160111%2F145249980956936361744dd.jpg%2F4pNWMDBP4RGolWCRuyEcsphE09emhZpy84KBZ_OCgWc%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=d00290e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n環球銀行金融電信協會（SWIFT）7月23日發佈的數據顯示，2020年6月，在基於金額統計的全球支付貨幣排名中，人民幣升至第五位，佔比為1.76%。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》報道，數據顯示，按月5月，人民幣支付金額總體增長了14.15％，同時，全球所有貨幣支付金額總體增長了16.05％。<br />\n<br />\n同期，以歐元區以外的國際支付作為統計口徑，人民幣位列第八，佔比1.14％。<br />\n<br />\n數據還顯示，主要貨幣的支付價值排名中，6月美元、歐元和英鎊分別以40.33%、34.10%和7.08%的佔比位居前三；日圓則以3.74%的份額排第四；而加元、港幣和澳元分別以1.75%、1.47%和1.44%的佔比位列第六至第八。<br />\n<br />\n若扣除歐元區內的支付，美元、歐元、日圓和英鎊仍穩居前四，佔比分別為45.32%、34.00%、4.48%和3.96%；第五至第七分別是加元的2.23%、澳元的1.51%和瑞郎的1.28%。"},{"pid":"eca3f0a8b787b7c62e00ece59ed918d1b3d1d7ff","tid":2122627,"uid":37874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76af3c2accee9b8ae9a84a50f158347962af6e71","tid":2122627,"uid":352851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:03:22.000Z","msg":"14億人嘅總數先多個700萬少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a28e83923f272853cff68dac1e9f3da097c8545","tid":2122627,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:10:05.000Z","msg":"中資行成日做9trade 刷㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}